ira, J.: Multimodal and adaptable medication assistant for the elderly: a prototype for interaction and usability in smartphones. In: Proceedings of 8th Iberian Conference on Information Systems and Technologies (CISTI), pp. 1&#8211;6 (2013)\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"Nielsen, J., Landauer, T.K.: A mathematical model of the finding of usability problems. In: Proceedings of INTERACT &#8217;93 and CHI &#8217;93, CHI &#8217;93, pp. 206&#8211;213. ACM, New York, NY, USA (1993)\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_journal_title=Univers. Access Inf. Soc.; citation_title=Age-related difference in the use of mobile phones; citation_author=J Zhou, P-L Rau, G Salvendy; citation_volume=13; citation_issue=4; citation_publication_date=2014; citation_pages=401-413; citation_doi=10.1007/s10209-013-0324-1; citation_id=CR51\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_journal_title=Univers. Access Inf. Soc.; citation_title=Worth-centred mobile phone design for older users; citation_author=K Renaud, J Biljon; citation_volume=9; citation_issue=4; citation_publication_date=2010; citation_pages=387-403; citation_doi=10.1007/s10209-009-0177-9; citation_id=CR52\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_reference\" content=\"citation_title=Wired for Speech: How Voice Activates and Advances the Human&#8211;Computer Relationship; citation_publication_date=2007; citation_id=CR53; citation_author=C Nass; citation_author=S Brave; citation_publisher=MIT Press\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_author\" content=\"Teixeira, Ant&#243;nio\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_author_email\" content=\"ajst@ua.pt\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_author_institution\" content=\"DETI &#8211; Department of Electronics, Telecommunications and Informatics, IEETA &#8211; Institute of Electronics and Telematics Engineering of Aveiro, University of Aveiro, Aveiro, Portugal\"/>\n\n    <meta name=\"citation_author\" content=\"Ferreira, Fl&#225;vio\"/>\n\n